Lesson 4
--------

This example illustrates a test of OFELI. It solves a
2-D transient heat equation using :

   - Triangle P1-finite element for space discretization
   - Implicit Euler scheme for time discretization
   - Mixed Dirichlet and Neumann Boundary Conditions

To execute the example type

          lesson4  test.dat

The program will then ask you for final time and time step.

